      <description>&lt;p&gt;Among this year&amp;rsquo;s tutorials at CVPR, Interpretable Machine Learning and Computer Vision was one of my favorite ones. The tutorial was about 2 hours and 45 minutes long, and was conducted by 4 amazing researchers. In this post I will try to summarize the key lessons in those lectures and will give a brief overview of the field in interpretable machine learning and explainable artificial intelligence (XAI).&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
